snippet.title: Kahoot!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official YouTube channel for Kahoot!, one of the world’s fastest growing learning brands. 

Millions around the world use Kahoot!’s free game-based learning platform each day to create, play and share fun learning games, in classrooms, at work and at home.

Subscribe to discover inspiring stories from our community, and stay on top of all the latest tips, tricks and tutorials to help you get the most out of Kahoot!

Join for FREE at www.kahoot.com
